data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!!! AND MOVE IN READY!!!!! $2,000 USE AS YOU CHOOSE!!!!! Seller is offering $2,000 towards closing cost, rate buy down, or whatever you choose. PLUS use our preferred lender and recieve an additional $1,000 lender credit. Welcome to the highly desired neighborhood of Sterling Farms. This 3-bedroom, 2-bath home built in 2021, features beautiful brand new luxory LVP flooring throughout. Upon entering the home you are greeted with the large foyer and spacious livingroom featuring beautiful vaulted ceiling. To the right of the livingroom is the dining area and the large open-concept kitchen. The family chef will be able to prepare meals while still being able to entertain guests. Adjacent to the livingroom and down the hall you will find two bedrooms and a full sized bathroom. Left of the livingroom is a large laundryroom and the master retreat seperate from the rest of the home. The master features a large walk in closet that is so big you will have to buy more clothes to fill it up. Treat yourself to a relaxing bath after those long days in the large garden tub in the master bath, or a long relaxing shower in the nice walk in shower. Head out back to the fully fenced private yard, where you have plenty of space to entertain or plant the family garden. This neighborhood features a community pool perfect for those hot summer days. Ready for your own private tour? Call your agent today.
